{"tid":1172446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會六四30周年遊行要求平反六四","createTime":"2019-05-26T12:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T13:06:08.000Z","uid":7828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c555ce6048f02e89c2f1cb21b42a0b199187dc","tid":1172446,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T12:23:38.000Z","msg":"支聯會舉行六四30周年遊行，今年除要求平反六四外，亦要求政府撤回逃犯條例修訂，支聯會表示有2200人參加，較去年多一倍，警方稱最高峰有2100人。<br />\n<br />\n每年六四前個多星期支聯會都會發起遊行，訴求始終如一，要求平反六四，由灣仔修頓遊行去中聯辦。<br />\n<br />\n六四事件過去三十年很多人都未敢忘記，亦希望下一代認識這段歷史。他剛由內地移居香港，當年都有參與天安門集會，首次來參加遊行。有人化身坦克車來悼念。<br />\n<br />\n在遊行隊伍當中，支聯會職員推着流動捐款箱收集遊行人士捐款，籌募日常經費。<br />\n<br />\n今年遊行加入要求政府撤回修訂逃犯條例，早前率團訪美的民主黨創黨主席李柱銘不同意外國勢力干預修例。<br />\n<br />\n遊行市民到達中聯辦在門外擺放六四三十的大型模型悼念，大批警員在現場維持秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=349374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349374&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BQb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=b9d96838\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349374&h=36c2752a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=349374</a>"},{"pid":"3a20d45412c236a55251da01076e62c04f97cd85","tid":1172446,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T12:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AfD3Q2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAfD3Q2a.jpg&h=efa3a349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利申 69出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb98b19ff5aed9c48fe119a34944c7b9ebf2d8d","tid":1172446,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"呢班傻撚真係<br />\n<br />\n有資源唔係優先畀當務之急嘅事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /